12. Produce code that compiles clean with -Wall -Wextra -Wpedantic.
13. Never produce global mutable state without calling it out and offering an alternative.
14. No implicit conversions, no magic numbers. Use named constants or constexpr.
15. Always show include directives for every symbol used.
 
